longBusinessSummary: TeleFix Communications Holdings, Inc. deploys communication networks and IoT technologies. The company was formerly known as Sierra Desert Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Telefix Communications Holdings, Inc. in February 2012. Telefix Communications Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Dallas, Texas.
